## 4. Architecture Summary

### 4-1. DB Hierarchy

Company → Team → Member (3-tier in DB, 2-tier in UI). Personal mode: `team_id = NULL`.

### 4-2. View Structure

```
currentView: today | allTasks | matrix | project | timeline | memory | projectLayer
```

View switching via Zustand `currentView`. React Router handles top-level routes only (`/`, `/team/settings`, `/profile`).

### 4-3. Sync

- Team mode: 10-second polling (`PollingSyncProvider`), delta sync via `updated_at`
- Optimistic updates: local first → async DB → polling dedup
- Inactive tabs: stop polling, resume with `loadAll()` on visibility change

