## 6. Banned Patterns

| # | Banned | Reason |
|---|--------|--------|
| 1 | `updateTask({...task})` | Signature violation. Use `updateTask(id, patch)` |
| 2 | Renaming existing tables/columns | Breaks entire system |
| 3 | Editing existing migration files | Breaks Supabase migration chain |
| 4 | `border-left` color borders on cards | Design system ban |
| 5 | `#c4c2ba`, `#d3d1c7` | Too faint. Min secondary text: `#888780` |
| 6 | Tables without RLS | Security violation |
| 7 | `getState()` to read store data in render | No re-render. Use `useStore` selectors |
| 8 | Modifying existing CSS files | Side-effect risk |
| 9 | Exposing VAPID private keys in conversation | Security violation |
